Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.61,0:22:42.34,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)\blur5}還剩下一個即將消失的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.57,0:22:47.61,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)\blur5}音も立てずに 今そっと
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.57,0:22:47.61,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)\blur5}現在悄悄地 沒有聲音的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.83,0:22:52.18,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)\blur5}あなたの夢のかけらが
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.83,0:22:52.18,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)\blur5}你的夢想的碎片
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.47,0:22:55.70,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)\blur5}Be Alive
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.47,0:22:55.70,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)\blur5}Be Alive
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.76,0:23:01.92,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)\blur5}もう　沈黙のままで　涙を隠さないで
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.76,0:23:01.92,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)\blur5}即使只能保持沉默 也不要隱藏眼淚
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.35,0:23:07.35,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)\blur5}繰り返されてく
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.35,0:23:07.35,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)\blur5}循環往復
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.61,0:23:09.47,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)\blur5}絶望の先に
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.61,0:23:09.47,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)\blur5}絕望的前方
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.61,0:23:16.60,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)\blur5}こころ　枯れても 明日を叫ぶのなら
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.61,0:23:16.60,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)\blur5}要是那顆枯萎的心 還能呼喚明天的話
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.85,0:23:20.67,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)\blur5}目の前は　きっと希望だ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.85,0:23:20.67,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)\blur5}眼前必將出現希望
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.53,0:23:30.55,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)\blur5}To Be Alive
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.53,0:23:30.55,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)\blur5}To Be Alive
